#!/usr/bin/env python3
"""
gen_routine_sheets.py - Dance Praktika floorcraft routine-sheet generator.

Renders printable PDF sheets that MIRROR THE INTERACTIVE BOARD 1:1 (no print flip):
  - raw board coordinates: x -> right, y -> down (origin top-left, like the board)
  - floor #f7f5f0 with 1 m grid; LOD arrows ring the floor counter-clockwise
  - couple-centre path drawn black at 60% opacity
  - dancers = oversized body ellipse + head + facing arrow (leader black, follower red)
  - each stamp carries a white/blue numbered badge; the live (End) couple is solid
  - figure-name labels honour `rot` / `br`; rhythm key (if present) sits inside the floor
  - landscape A4; colours/fonts synced to the board (Montserrat / DM Mono if installed)

Usage:  python3 gen_routine_sheets.py
        SHEETS_OUTDIR=~/studioplanner/docs python3 gen_routine_sheets.py
        python3 gen_routine_sheets.py Foxtrot_Newcomer_Routine_1
"""
